### 로그인 (카카오/네이버/애플)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "kakao",
  "accessToken": "소셜_액세스_토큰"
}

### 토큰 갱신
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 로그아웃
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
